         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 1769, recto: (1) There have been allotted to Pamonthes, son of Totoes, (2) of the field of Kalasiris, son of Pamonthes, (3) the strategos, which is ceded (4) at 1/2 (artaba of) wheat to 1 arura of land -----. (5) They have been ceded to Pamonthes, son of (6) ----- (7) ----- highland arura 1/2, (artaba of) wheat 2 1/12 (8) / wheat 1 1/24 again. Signed, (9) Pikos, [in year] 30.</ab>
